message.body: Hey chic, are you up for a bite and a beer tonight around 7:30?
Oh man... You have no idea how much I want to say yes to that, but I have class tomorrow and I still have reading to finish for it!!
Thanks for thinking of me, I would love to see you. Raincheck for sure!
Oh, I so understand! Sorry to tempt! We'll make a rain check. :)
